<h1 class="fw7 f1 fl w-100 mt2 mb3 font-primary font-dark lh-title">Emotar</h1>
</div>

<div class="w-100 w-50-ns fn fl-ns">
<p>Emotar takes a photo of you and then converts it into a 3D model to be used in GIFs. Uncanny valley? Yep. Loads of fun? Definitely.</p>
<a class="button" href="https://medium.com/@kevin8ma/redesigning-htcs-emotar-4a7e719f87c3">Full Case Study</a>
</div>
</div>

<p>Emotar is a mobile app by HTC R&amp;D, that aims to help users create personalized stickers for instant messaging apps. I worked with a project manager and 2 developers on shipping the next version.</p>

<!-- <video loop  name="Sticker" src="/assets/img/htc/sticker.mp4" autoplay="autoplay"></video> -->

<div class="mhn2" style="
    margin-left: -20%;
